Wude Ayalew Yimer (Amharic; amụrụ na 4 Julaị, na afọ 1987) bụ onye Etiopia ọkachamara na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge
Ọ bụ onye nwetara ọla nchara karịa mita 10,000 na 2009 World Championships in Athletics ma were ọlaọcha na ihe omume ahụ na afọ 2011 All-Africa Games
Nwanne ya nwanyị Hiwot Ayalew bụkwa onye na-agba ọsọ n'ọkwa kachasị elu.
Na afọ 2006 World Cross Country Championships ọ mechara nke ise na ogologo ọsọ, ebe ndị otu Etiopia, nke Yimer so na ya, meriri asọmpi otu
Ọ bụ onye nke ise na mita 5000 na afọ 2006 World Junior Championships
Ọ mechiri oge ahụ site na mmeri Cross Internacional de Venta de Baños site na ihe karịrị 25 sekọnd.
Na afo 2009 World Championships in Athletics na Berlin, ọ meriri ọla nchara na 10,000 mita ọsọ
Na afọ 2010 World 10K Bangalore na Mee, o setịpụrụ ndekọ ọhụrụ nke 31:58 mgbe ọ kụrụ onye mmeri na-agbachitere Aselefech Mergia na njedebe ikpeazụ.

O sonyere na asọmpi Beach to Beacon na Cape Elizabeth, Maine n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ ma bụrụ onye nke abụọ n'azụ Lineth Chepkurui. Ya na onye Kenya ahụ gbanwere ọnọdụ na Falmouth Road Race ụbọchị asatọ ka e mesịrị, na-emeri mmeri n'elu kilomita asaa na oge nke 35:46. Na Delhi Half Marathon, ọ gwụchara n'ọnọdụ nke atọ maka nke abụọ n'usoro n'ime afọ abụọ na ihe omume ahụ.

Na 2011 IAAF World Cross Country Championships, ọ nọ n'ọnọdụ nke isii ma nyere ụmụ nwanyị Etiopia aka inweta ihe nrite ọlaọcha n'akụkụ Meselech Melkamu. O sonyeghị na ndị otu World Championships, mana a họpụtara ya maka afọ 2011 All-Africa Games, ebe ọ bụ onye nke abụọ na Sule Utura site na nkeji nke abụọ. Ọ mechiri afọ ahụ site na onye nke abụọ n'azụ Priscah Jeptoo na Saint Silvester Road Race. O ruru n'elu ikpo okwu na Cross de Itálica na Jenụwarị 2012, na-ewere ọnọdụ nke atọ n'azụ Linet Masai na Vivian Cheruiyot, wee merie Elgoibar Cross Country otu izu ka e mesịrị. O meriri Saint Silvester Road Race na afọ 2014, na-emechi afọ ise ụmụ nwanyị Kenya.
